INSERT INTO tourist_sites (trip_id, name, address, visit_date, visit_time, notes, website, created_at, updated_at) VALUES
-- Day 7 Evening
(30001, 'Stephansplatz Walking Tour', 'Stephansplatz, 1010 Vienna, Austria', 1788822000000, '19:00', 'Evening walk around St. Stephen''s Cathedral square', 'https://www.wien.info/en/sightseeing/sights/from-a-to-z/st-stephen-s-cathedral-382858', NOW(), NOW()),

-- Day 8 Morning
(30001, 'Schönbrunn Palace', 'Schönbrunner Schloßstraße 47, 1130 Vienna, Austria', 1788870600000, '08:30', 'Arrive early (08:30) to enjoy the gardens and Gloriette. Grand Tour of palace rooms if time permits.', 'https://www.schoenbrunn.at/en/', NOW(), NOW()),

-- Day 8 Afternoon
(30001, 'Naschmarkt', 'Naschmarkt, 1060 Vienna, Austria', 1788883200000, '12:00', 'Tour the food stalls and have lunch at one of the market restaurants (NENI or local fish restaurants)', 'https://www.naschmarkt-vienna.com/', NOW(), NOW()),

(30001, 'Hofburg Palace', 'Michaelerkuppel, 1010 Vienna, Austria', 1788894000000, '15:00', 'Imperial Palace complex in the city center', 'https://www.hofburg-wien.at/en/', NOW(), NOW()),

(30001, 'Austrian National Library', 'Josefsplatz 1, 1015 Vienna, Austria', 1788895800000, '15:30', 'Magnificent State Hall library', 'https://www.onb.ac.at/en/', NOW(), NOW()),

-- Day 8 Evening
(30001, 'Grinzing Wine Village', 'Grinzing, 1190 Vienna, Austria', 1788908400000, '19:00', 'Take tram 38. Short walk through the village streets and dinner at a Heuriger (wine tavern) with live music and September Sturm wine', 'https://www.wien.info/en/locations/grinzing-383124', NOW(), NOW());
